#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/product_management/product_tracking/lots.rst:280
msgid ""
"To create a lot number for a product, begin by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> Products --> Lot/Serial Numbers`, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
