#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:86
msgid ""
"To ensure seamless Sendcloud integration with Odoo, :ref:`install <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-module>` and :ref:`link <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/link-sendcloud-module>` the Sendcloud shipping connector "
"to the Sendcloud account. Then, :ref:`configure Odoo fields <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-shipping-info>`, so Sendcloud can accurately "
"pull shipping data to generate labels."
msgstr ""
"כדי להבטיח אינטגרציה חלקה של Sendcloud עם Odoo,‏ :ref:`התקינו <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-module>` ו:ref:`קשרו <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/link-sendcloud-module>` את מחבר המשלוח של Sendcloud "
"לחשבון Sendcloud. לאחר מכן, ‏:ref:`הגדירו שדות Odoo <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/sendcloud-shipping-info>`, כדי ש-Sendcloud יוכל למשוך "
"בדיוק נתוני משלוח ליצירת תוויות."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:94
msgid ""
":ref:`Enable pickup points on websites <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"sendcloud-pickups>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`הפעלת נקודות איסוף באתרים <inventory/shipping_receiving/sendcloud-"
"pickups>`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:99
msgid "Install Sendcloud shipping module"
msgstr "התקנת מודול משלוח Sendcloud"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:101
msgid ""
"After the Sendcloud account is set up and configured, it's time to configure "
"the Odoo database. To get started, go to Odoo's :guilabel:`Apps` module, "
"search for the `Sendcloud Shipping` integration, and install it."
msgstr ""
"לאחר הקמה והגדרת חשבון Sendcloud, הגיע הזמן להגדיר את מסד הנתונים של Odoo. "
"כדי להתחיל, עברו למודול‏ :guilabel:`יישומים` של Odoo, חפשו את האינטגרציה "
"`Sendcloud Shipping` והתקינו אותה."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:None
msgid "Sendcloud Shipping module in the Odoo Apps module."
msgstr "מודול Sendcloud Shipping במודול יישומים של Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:112
msgid "Sendcloud shipping connector configuration"
msgstr "הגדרת מחבר משלוח Sendcloud"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:114
msgid ""
"Once installed, activate the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Shipping` module "
"in :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"The :guilabel:`Sendcloud Connector` setting is found under "
"the :guilabel:`Shipping Connectors` section."
msgstr ""
"לאחר ההתקנה, הפעילו את המודול‏ :guilabel:`Sendcloud Shipping` "
"ב:menuselection:`מלאי --> תצורה --> הגדרות`. ההגדרה‏ :guilabel:`Sendcloud "
"Connector` נמצאת תחת הקטע‏ :guilabel:`מחברי משלוח`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:118
msgid ""
"After activating the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Connector`, click on "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Shipping Methods` link below the listed connector. "
"Once on the :guilabel:`Shipping Methods` page, click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"לאחר הפעלת‏ :guilabel:`Sendcloud Connector`, לחצו על הקישור‏ :guilabel:`שיטות "
"משלוח Sendcloud` מתחת למחבר הרשום. ברגע שאתם בעמוד‏ :guilabel:`שיטות משלוח`, "
"לחצו על‏ :guilabel:`חדש`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:123
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Shipping Methods` can also be accessed by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Delivery --> Shipping "
"Methods`."
msgstr ""
"‏:guilabel:`שיטות משלוח` ניתן גם לגשת על ידי מעבר אל‏ :menuselection:`מלאי --> "
"תצורה --> משלוח --> שיטות משלוח`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:126
msgid ""
"Fill out the following fields in the :guilabel:`New Shipping Method` form:"
msgstr "מלאו את השדות הבאים בטופס‏ :guilabel:`שיטת משלוח חדשה`:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:128
msgid ":guilabel:`Shipping Method`: type `Sendcloud DPD`."
msgstr "‏:guilabel:`שיטת משלוח`: הקלידו `Sendcloud DPD`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:129
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Provider`: select :guilabel:`Sendcloud` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr "‏:guilabel:`ספק`: בחרו‏ :guilabel:`Sendcloud` מהתפריט הנפתח."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Product`: set the product that was configured for this "
"shipping method or create a new product."
msgstr ""
"‏:guilabel:`מוצר משלוח`: הגדירו את המוצר שהוגדר עבור שיטת משלוח זו או צרו "
"מוצר חדש."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:132
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` tab, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Public Key`."
msgstr ""
"בכרטיסייה‏ :guilabel:`תצורת SendCloud`, הזינו את‏ :guilabel:`מפתח ציבורי של "
"Sendcloud`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:133
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` tab, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Sendcloud Secret Key`."
msgstr ""
"בכרטיסייה‏ :guilabel:`תצורת SendCloud`, הזינו את‏ :guilabel:`מפתח סודי של "
"Sendcloud`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:138
msgid "Pickup points"
msgstr "נקודות איסוף"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:140
msgid ""
"Sendcloud's `service point delivery <https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/"
"articles/360026097951-FAQ-Service-Points>`_ lets customers choose a pickup "
"location (such as a nearby shop or locker) instead of entering a private "
"delivery address."
msgstr ""
"שירות `משלוח לנקודת שירות‏ <https://support.sendcloud.com/hc/en-us/articles/"
"360026097951-FAQ-Service-Points>`_ של Sendcloud מאפשר ללקוחות לבחור מיקום "
"איסוף (כמו חנות סמוכה או לוקר) במקום להזין כתובת משלוח פרטית."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:145
msgid ""
"To enable the feature, go to the shipping method form, and in "
"the :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` tab, under the :guilabel:`Options` "
"section, enable :guilabel:`Use Sendcloud Locations` feature."
msgstr ""
"כדי להפעיל את התכונה, עברו לטופס שיטת המשלוח, ובכרטיסייה‏ :guilabel:`תצורת "
"SendCloud`, תחת הקטע‏ :guilabel:`אפשרויות`, הפעילו את התכונה‏ :guilabel:`השתמש "
"במיקומי Sendcloud`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:150
msgid ""
"Pickup point selection is only available through the **Website** app (the "
"online checkout view). It is not currently possible to select a pickup point "
"manually through the **Sales** app (the internal database view)."
msgstr ""
"בחירת נקודת איסוף זמינה רק דרך אפליקציית **אתר** (תצוגת התשלום המקוונת). "
"כרגע לא ניתן לבחור נקודת איסוף באופן ידני דרך אפליקציית **מכירות** (תצוגת "
"מסד הנתונים הפנימית)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:154
msgid ""
"For example, if the customer selects a shipping method like *Sendcloud "
"Mondial Relay*, they must choose a pickup point during the checkout process "
"on the website. If no pickup point is selected, the delivery order cannot be "
"validated in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"לדוגמה, אם הלקוח בוחר שיטת משלוח כמו *Sendcloud Mondial Relay*, הוא חייב "
"לבחור נקודת איסוף במהלך תהליך התשלום באתר. אם לא נבחרה נקודת איסוף, לא ניתן "
"לאמת את הזמנת המשלוח ב-Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:159
