"או ליצור חדש על ידי לחיצה על :guilabel:`חדש`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/replenishment/reordering_rules.rst:59
msgid ""
"On the product form, under the :guilabel:`General Information` tab, set "
"the :guilabel:`Product Type` to :guilabel:`Storable Product`. This is "
"necessary because Odoo only tracks stock quantities for storable products, "
"and quantities are needed to trigger reordering rules."
msgstr ""

